snippet.title: Metal: Hellsinger VR - Official Demo Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description:
Lead vocalist Matt Heafy of the metal band Trivium gives an update on Metal: Hellsinger VR, revealing a demo is available now for the upcoming metal rhythm shooter game. The demo includes the first two levels and features artists Mikael Stanne of Dark Tranquility and Alissa White-Gluz of Arch Enemy. Metal: Hellsinger VR will be available on Meta Quest, PSVR2, and SteamVR in fall 2024.

#IGN #Gaming
